Mouse Events.

    - when ever we perform mouse events automatically coresponding
      directives will be executed by Angular Framework.

Syntax.

ng-mousedown /
ng-mouseup   /

ng-mouseover /      = "user defined function"
ng-mouseout  /

ng-mouseenter/
ng-mouseleave


ng-cloak.
    used to avoid the flickering effect on web pages.

[Note . ng-clock directive will work with Angular 1.6.3 with bower components ]


